Provides: libidzebra1.4-mod-grs-xml, libidzebra1.4-mod-grs-regx, libidzebra1.4-mod-marc, libidzebra1.4-mod-danbib
Description: IDZebra modules 
 This virtual package contains all base IDZebra filter modules.
 .
